description:
Vanica and her subordinates continue their attack on the Heart Kingdom. Meanwhile, back at the Black Bulls` hideout, Captain Yami`s fight against Dante continued. Despite how overwhelmingly powerful Dante is, Yami continues to fight back, landing another powerful blow onto Dante. However, no matter how much Dante is damaged, he continues to regenerate. What will Yami do?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: 団長 ヤミ・スケヒロ
